"ngram\": \"her arms\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 882}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 903}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Few Olympians in Paris this week have begun a final under this much pressure.\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 983, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 923, \"end\": 928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.9400585924103807e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Few Olympians\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"this much pressure\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 982}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nemour was not just the overwhelming favourite on the uneven bars but carried the expectations of two countries and one continent on her shoulders.\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nemour\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 990}, {\"ngram\": \"just the overwhelming favourite\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"the uneven bars\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1049}, {\"ngram\": \"the expectations\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"two countries\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"one continent\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1113}, {\"ngram\": \"her shoulders\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was born and raised in France, and still lives and trains near her small town, Saint-Benoit-la-Foret.\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1159, \"end\": 1165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7023128176538608, \"rank\": 0.4238376870276573, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her small town\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But last year she switched to represent her father's nation, Algeria, after a dispute with French Gymnastics.\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1299, \"end\": 1306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9735587488803565, \"rank\": 0.026896976522587858, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 1329, \"end\": 1335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.938855118089448, \"rank\": 0.06503321721856749, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1336, \"end\": 1346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.999546667422881, \"rank\": 0.00045353818076231795, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her father's nation\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1297}, {\"ngram\": \"a dispute\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A few moments laterher gold medal was confirmed.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"laterher gold medal\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She unfurled an Algerian flag and wrapped herself up in the white and green colours, and the Parisian crowd greeted her like one of their own.\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1414, \"end\": 1427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Algeria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Algerian flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.or