48}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic medal\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reigning Olympic champion, Belgium's Nina Derwael, set an early target with a score of 14.766, but that was soon eclipsed by the world champion, China's Qui Qiyuan, who executed a routine with a difficulty value of 7.2, the highest of any athlete on any apparatus yet at the Games, to score 15.500.\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2483, \"end\": 2490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9649257287268415, \"rank\": 0.03634918320300154, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 2493, \"end\": 2505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nina_Derwael\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nina Derwael\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nina_Derwael\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nina_Derwael\"}, {\"begin\": 2601, \"end\": 2606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999196436020122, \"rank\": 8.030640923656383e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The reigning Olympic champion\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2481}, {\"ngram\": \"an early target\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2526}, {\"ngram\": \"a score\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2539}, {\"ngram\": \"the world champion\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"a routine\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2643}, {\"ngram\": \"a difficulty value\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2667}, {\"ngram\": \"any athlete\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2702}, {\"ngram\": \"any apparatus\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nemour's routine matched that difficulty, which meant she needed to beat Qui's execution for gold.\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2854, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nemour's routine\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2772}, {\"ngram\": \"that difficulty\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"Qui's execution\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2844}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2853}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I saw the score of the Chinese, I said to myself that I will have to go there and bring out the routine of my life,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2855, \"to\": 2987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2884, \"end\": 2891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9642677606378772, \"rank\": 0.03703430549344239, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the score\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"the routine\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 2964}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 2975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the seconds before she began, Nemour took a few deep breaths.\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the seconds\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3003}, {\"ngram\": \"Nemour\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3028}, {\"ngram\": \"a few deep breaths\", \"from\": 3034, \"to\": 3052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She chalked her hands while her coach Marc Tcherlinko, who discovered her at a young age in her local gym, gave her one final pep talk.\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her hands\", \"from\": 3066, \"to\": 3075}, {\"ngram\": \"her coach\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3091}, {\"ngram\": \"Marc Tcherlinko\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"a young age\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3142}, {\"ngram\": \"her local gym\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3159}, {\"ngram\": \"one final pep talk\", \"from\": 3170, \"to\": 3188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then she ran and leapt into her routine, and from there on she was in her own bubble, oblivious to the roars of \\\"allez!\\\"\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3310, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her routine\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3229}, {\"ngram\": \"her own bubble\", \"from\": 3260, \"to\": 3274}, {\"ngram\": \"the roars\", \"from\": 3289, \"to\": 3298}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"allez\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"echoing around the hall.\", \"from\": 3311, \"to\": 3335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hall\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That is what I did.\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3357, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I got the best score of my life.\\\"\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3391, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best score\", \"from\": 3364, \"to\": 3378}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her score, 15.700, was reward not just for her performance but for what she had been through to get to the Games.\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her score\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3402}, {\"ngram\": \"reward\", \"from\": 3416, \"to\": 3422}, {\"ngram\": \"her performance\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3451}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3496, \"to\": 3505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Somewhere up in the VIP boxes, some executives of French Gymnastics wearing soft shoes and crisp polo shirts were probably watching on, wondering how such a prodigious talent got away.\", \"from\": 3508, \"to\": 3692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3558, \"end\": 3564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.938855118089448, \"rank\": 0.06503321721856749, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_languag